The field can have many values selected from a set. e.g.:
    "2114298810": [
      {
        "name": null,
        "value": "null"
      },
      {
        "name": "Coffee Host",
        "value": "78"
      },
      {
        "name": "Worship",
        "value": "145"
      }
    ]
    Note that there always seems to be one empty entry.
